General Assembly Senate Resolution No. 9
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 3099
Referred to Committee on Executive and Legislative Nominations
Introduced by:
SEN. DUFF, 25th Dist.
RESOLUTION CONFIRMING THE NOMINATION OF JOSHUA WOJCIK
OF BROOKLYN TO BE SECRETARY OF THE OFFICE OF POLICY
AND MANAGEMENT.
Resolved by the Senate:
1 That the nomination by His Excellency, the Governor, of Joshua
2 Wojcik of Brooklyn, to be Secretary of the Office of Policy and
3 Management, to serve at the pleasure of the Governor, but not longer
4 than March 1, 2027, is hereby approved and confirmed.
LCO No. 3099 1 of 1

